author: fmeschbe
msg: FELIX-3874 Fix Inventory Printer Activator class name
The Inventory Printer BundleActivator has been renamed so the constant
to load the class through reflection has to be changed. Otherwise the
all-in-one WebConsole bundle will not start the Inventory Printer.
